{"tid":1878013,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"尖沙咀吾見銀包","createTime":"2020-02-13T10:49:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T10:55:35.000Z","uid":329027,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"610b4d4a1834330ce3e349375f9b5765c0ab5707","tid":1878013,"uid":329027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T10:49:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pfhJ5k8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpfhJ5k8.png&h=70274f50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係個Gregory藍花銀包 魔術貼摺得嘅😭<br />\n前幾日同朋友食完飯 去左嘉乎中心隔離夾公仔 <br />\n因為我帶左個細袋 又急住去廁所 就將個銀包放左係個膠袋入面 擺左係朋友腳邊 冇同佢講銀包係入面 之後去撘車先知吾見 😭😭 其實已經報失 但有fd同我講 有啲人汁到都吾想攞去警局 驚信吾過 所以我先煩 現金冇吾緊要 其實最想要反張相同身份證 仲未去到入境處整😭🙏🏽🙏🏽感激有心人"},{"pid":"b54bfc73348d4bb1e1cc5d9b9d6415f563fb82cf","tid":1878013,"uid":316537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T10:50:22.000Z","msg":"吾你老母"},{"pid":"d61535bd66ff539237144458abb402d083c2529a","tid":1878013,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T10:50:33.000Z","msg":"😭"},{"pid":"f6e0f4695123b613554787399ecc76b7361f1491","tid":1878013,"uid":329027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T10:55:35.000Z","msg":"求好心人🙏🏽🙏🏽🙏🏽😭"}]}